Law from the University of So Paulo (USP) in 2000. Graduated in Business from Fundao Getulio Vargas (EAESP/FGV) in 1996, spent one semester as an exchange student at the University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC). Hired by INSPER as a LLM professor, currently holds the position of General Counsel of Goldman Sachs Brazil and Chief Operating Officer (COO) for the Brazil office. serving on several management and control side committees. Joined Goldman Sachs as a Vice President in 2011 and was named Managing Director in 2015. Prior to joining the firm, he was an external counsel in banking and securities in So Paulo for 13 years, from trainee to partner at external law firms. Currently acting as the vice president of the Legal Committee of ANBIMA (the Brazilian Financial and Capital Markets Association), the head of the Legal Committee of ABBI (the International Bank Association in Brazil) and a member of the Advisory Chamber on Regulation and Market Supervision of B3, the Brazilian exchange. Experience on private law, banking and securities, corporate law, financial products, as well as COO of investment bank and broker dealer."/><ENDERECO FLAG-DE-PREFERENCIA="ENDERECO_INSTITUCIONAL"><ENDERECO-PROFISSIONAL CODIGO-INSTITUICAO-EMPRESA="000100000991" NOME-INSTITUICAO-EMPRESA="Goldman Sachs do Brasil Banco Mltiplo S.A." CODIGO-ORGAO="000101000995" NOME-ORGAO="Diretoria Jurdica" CODIGO-UNIDADE="" NOME-UNIDADE="" LOGRADOURO-COMPLEMENTO="Rua Leopoldo Couto de Magalhes Jnior, 700 - 17o andar" PAIS="Brasil" UF="SP" CEP="04542000" CIDADE="So Paulo" BAIRRO="Itaim Bibi" DDD="11" TELEFONE="33720241" RAMAL="" FAX="" CAIXA-POSTAL="" HOME-PAGE=""/></ENDERECO><FORMACAO-ACADEMICA-TITULACAO><GRADUACAO SEQUENCIA-FORMACAO="2" NIVEL="1" TITULO-DO-TRABALHO-DE-CONCLUSAO-DE-CURSO="no aplicvel" NOME-DO-ORIENTADOR="no aplicvel" CODIGO-INSTITUICAO="000400000008" NOME-INSTITUICAO="Fundao Getlio Vargas" CODIGO-ORGAO="" NOME-ORGAO="" CODIGO-CURSO="60444924" NOME-CURSO="Administrao Pblica" CODIGO-AREA-C